Primarily responsible for recruiting talent for Schwab Technology Services. Positions include: Program Directors, Project Managers, Project Coordinators, Business Analysts, Technical Architects, Software Applications Engineers (Java, C#, .NET) and Software QA Engineers.

Worked closely with Healthcare clients in the Phoenix area on their technology road maps and resource plans. Assisted team of Recruiters in the sourcing, screening and placement of top Healthcare IT talent to help the organizations achieve the required criteria and standards in Adoption and Meaningful Use. Offered a broad range of capabilities in supporting the IT transformation of all technology initiatives on full life cycle EMR/EHR implementations, post “Go Live” support, end user training, interoperability, HIPAA 5010 and ICD-10. TEKsystems provides support with the following: Network Engineering, Systems Administration, Business Applications, Clinical Systems, HL7 Interface Analysis & Development, EMR/EHR Design, Build & Analysis, Project Management & Training, Unified Communications, Virtualization, Storage, Security, WAN/LAN Optimization, Windows 7 Deployment

Specialized in placing IT professionals with healthcare-specific experience.  From ICD-10 and EHR-driven regulatory mandates to the emergence of Big Data and mobility, technology is driving the future of healthcare.  Healthcare payer and provider organizations offer a wide variety of IT healthcare jobs to talented IT professionals seeking rewarding opportunities that improve patient care and public health.

Responsible for building consultant relationships, understanding the local employment market and consulting with technical candidates to help them advance their careers. Specialized in placing applications, network infrastructure and IT support professionals on engagements aligned with their skills, goals and interests.

Responsible for building client relationships, understanding the local labor market, and consulting with clients to implement the most effective talent attraction and retention strategies. Managed a team of recruiters and conducted employee evaluations.

summary: Senior Talent Advisor with expertise in identifying talent and performing full life-cycle recruiting. Focused on delivering the best talent acquisition experience to business partners and candidates.
